  "text": "The economic losses due to bluetongue is around 3 billion US$ per year in the world [CITATION_1] . The direct losses are death, abortions, weight loss and reduced milk and meat productions and indirect losses are export restrictions of live animals, semen and foetal calf serum [CITATION_2] .",
